    <info type="text">Detects Request to amsiInitFailed that can be used to disable AMSI Scanning. </info>
    <info type="link">https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/08ca62cc8860f4660e945805d0dd615ce75258c1/rules/windows/process_creation/win_powershell_amsi_bypass.yml</info>
